                                      int indexEnd,

        Returns first index where data has values that meet threshold for at least winLength samples in a row
        Parameters:
        data - input column
        indexBegin - index to begin search
        indexEnd - index where search ends
        threshold - value that data entry must be above
        winLength - entries must be above treshold for winLength in a row

        firstIndex first index of series of entries that meet threshold

      • searchMultiContinuityWithinRange

        public java.util.List<org.dkchallenge.IndexPair> searchMultiContinuityWithinRange​(java.util.List<java.lang.Double> data,
                                                                                  int indexBegin,
                                                                                  int indexEnd,
                                                                                  double thresholdLo,
                                                                                  double thresholdHi,
                                                                                  int winLength)
        Returns all sets of entries that meet threshold
        Parameters:
        data - input column
        indexBegin - index to begin search
        indexEnd - index where search ends
        thresholdHi - value that data entry must be above
        thresholdLo - value that data entry must be below
        winLength - entries must be above threshold for winLength in a row
        Returns:
        indices returns List of entry series that meet threshold as Pair. Each pair contains first and last element in each series.
